WEBVTT

1
00:00:52.465 --> 00:00:56.333 line:82%
This is London. The world's
greatest city.

2
00:00:58.098 --> 00:00:59.875 line:82%
I've lived here for 22 years.

3
00:01:01.025 --> 00:01:03.117 line:82%
Every morning I walk down
the same street.

4
00:01:03.620 --> 00:01:06.208 line:82%
And every morning, the street
asks who I am.

5
00:01:07.495 --> 00:01:09.917 line:82%
It asks: "Who is Chaudhary
Baldev Singh?

6
00:01:10.672 --> 00:01:12.942 line:82%
Where is he from?
Why is he here?"

7
00:01:14.755 --> 00:01:16.298 line:82%
How should I answer this?

8
00:01:17.257 --> 00:01:22.378 line:82%
I've spent half my life here, yet
this land and I are still strangers.

9
00:01:23.788 --> 00:01:27.462 line:82%
No one knows me here,
except these pigeons.

10
00:01:28.255 --> 00:01:29.750 line:82%
They're like me.

11
00:01:31.192 --> 00:01:32.750 line:82%
They have no country either.

12
00:01:33.383 --> 00:01:36.792 line:82%
Wherever they spot grain,
they eat it and take flight.

13
00:01:38.392 --> 00:01:41.038 line:82%
When will I be able to fly away?
I don't know.

14
00:01:42.310 --> 00:01:44.292 line:82%
Necessity has clipped my wings.

15
00:01:44.993 --> 00:01:47.042 line:82%
And the need to eat
has chained my feet.

16
00:01:48.150 --> 00:01:52.125 line:82%
But one day, I will definitely
go back to our country.

17
00:01:54.578 --> 00:01:56.083 line:82%
To our Punjab.

18
00:02:06.390 --> 00:02:11.917 line:82%
When you hear the cuckoo's cry,
memories like bullets fly

19
00:02:25.708 --> 00:02:30.861 line:82%
Come home, stranger,
your country calls you

20
