The illiterate souls of the
village can't read your letter

26
00:03:54.307 --> 00:04:01.161 line:82%
If you come and kiss the
motherland, then it'll be happy

27
00:04:01.394 --> 00:04:07.074 line:82%
We agree that you have your
dreams, but we're your own

28
