Glory to Goddess Lakshmi!

33
00:04:48.725 --> 00:04:51.125 line:82%
Yes, Lajjo. I got here safely.

34
00:04:51.558 --> 00:04:53.292 line:82%
OK, I'll hang up.

35
00:05:08.518 --> 00:05:10.500 line:82%
What's so funny this morning,
Chutki?

36
00:05:13.007 --> 00:05:17.530 line:82%
For the past 20 years, Dad's gone
to the same place.

37
00:05:17.613 --> 00:05:22.050 line:82%
But every day you phone and ask:
"Did you get there safely?"

38
00:05:22.410 --> 00:05:25.967 line:82%
You wouldn't understand.
It's a habit.

39
00:05:26.150 --> 00:05:28.035 line:82%
Miss Lucy is right.

40
00:05:28.118 --> 00:05:31.793 line:82%
"If you can't change your habits,
soon they'll become needs."

41
00:05:32.291 --> 00:05:36.835 line:82%
More philosophy? Why can't you
talk like a 12-year-old?

42
00:05:37.172 --> 00:05:38.959 line:82%
Why talk like a grown up?

43
00:05:39.042 --> 00:05:42.460 line:82%
Oh, Mom! Childhood and youth
mean nothing.

44
00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:48.257 line:82%
A person's age depends entirely
on how they feel inside.

45
00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:50.581 line:82%
All right, I give up.

46
00:05:50.664 --> 00:05:52.868 line:82%
Go to school and pick
Miss Lucy's brain instead.

47
