- Ok?
- Ok, Mom.

48
00:05:55.827 --> 00:05:58.418 line:82%
Why do you forget to eat
your almonds?

49
00:05:58.667 --> 00:06:00.736 line:82%
What can I do? It's a habit.

50
00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.126 line:82%
Bye, Mom.

51
