a complete stranger

54
00:06:28.150 --> 00:06:29.390 line:82%
has come
into my thoughts

55
00:06:29.597 --> 00:06:33.084 line:82%
That's my diary.
Only I can read it.

56
00:06:33.167 --> 00:06:35.252 line:82%
It's so interesting.
Let me read it.

57
00:06:35.481 --> 00:06:37.709 line:82%
No way, it's private.

58
00:06:37.960 --> 00:06:39.717 line:82%
Private? For me, too?

59
00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:44.293 line:82%
When a girl grows up, she becomes
her mother's friend, too.

60
00:06:45.303 --> 00:06:46.651 line:82%
You won't tell anyone?

61
00:06:46.992 --> 00:06:48.000 line:82%
Never.

62
00:06:48.083 --> 00:06:49.502 line:82%
- Promise?
- Yes, promise.

63
00:06:50.456 --> 00:06:52.218 line:82%
I'll read and you listen.

64
00:06:52.739 --> 00:06:53.980 line:82%
Alright.

65
