For the first time in 18 years

66
00:07:08.125 --> 00:07:11.960 line:82%
a complete stranger comes
into my thoughts.

67
00:07:14.125 --> 00:07:17.711 line:82%
A shadow flutters past my eyes.

68
00:07:19.250 --> 00:07:22.795 line:82%
Someone taps at my heart's door.

69
00:07:24.068 --> 00:07:27.752 line:82%
His dark deep eyes ask me
to surrender.

70
00:07:29.045 --> 00:07:30.413 line:82%
The lines on my palm

71
00:07:31.583 --> 00:07:32.911 line:82%
turn into his face.

72
00:07:33.250 --> 00:07:37.168 line:82%
His silken breath
caresses my cheeks.

73
00:07:38.250 --> 00:07:41.752 line:82%
The scent of his hands
lingers in my hair.

74
00:07:42.727 --> 00:07:47.460 line:82%
Yes. For the first time in 18 years

75
00:07:48.333 --> 00:07:51.905 line:82%
a complete stranger
comes into my thoughts.

76
00:07:57.167 --> 00:07:59.960 line:82%
Simi, I didn't know you were
such a good poet.

77
00:08:00.545 --> 00:08:03.501 line:82%
The boy sounds wonderful.
Who is he?

78
00:08:04.577 --> 00:08:07.418 line:82%
Unknown. Unseen.

79
00:08:07.875 --> 00:08:10.085 line:82%
You mean he doesn't exist?

80
00:08:10.750 --> 00:08:13.542 line:82%
If you ask me, you can't
find such boys.

81
00:08:14.650 --> 00:08:18.418 line:82%
You're crazy. You don't even know
him, and you dream of him?

82
00:08:22.083 --> 00:08:25.043 line:82%
No, Ma. This isn't a dream.

83
00:08:26.942 --> 00:08:30.501 line:82%
I know I've never met him
or seen him.

84
