01:06:07.708 --> 01:06:09.127 line:82%
I'm an Indian man.

676
01:06:10.459 --> 01:06:13.836 line:82%
And I know what honor means
to an Indian woman.

677
01:06:15.335 --> 01:06:18.420 line:82%
I wouldn't take advantage of you,
not in my wildest dreams.

678
01:06:19.667 --> 01:06:22.959 line:82%
Please believe me,
I'm telling you the truth.

679
01:06:23.958 --> 01:06:28.918 line:82%
Nothing happened last night.
It was only a joke.

680
01:06:30.875 --> 01:06:31.876 line:82%
Believe me.

681
01:06:39.959 --> 01:06:43.794 line:82%
Don't joke like that. I don't know
what I would've done.

682
01:06:44.459 --> 01:06:45.917 line:82%
Never joke like that again.

683
01:06:46.584 --> 01:06:47.626 line:82%
I am sorry.

684
01:06:49.333 --> 01:06:52.650 line:82%
I'll never do it again,
I promise... I'm sorry.

685
01:07:15.747 --> 01:07:18.472 line:82%
Hurry, get dressed.
We have a bus to catch.

686
01:07:19.833 --> 01:07:21.983 line:82%
Can I have my shirt back?

687
01:07:40.548 --> 01:07:43.500 line:82%
The bus leaves in ten minutes.
Want something to eat?

688
01:07:45.583 --> 01:07:47.000 line:82%
No, I'm not hungry.

689
01:07:51.615 --> 01:07:53.858 line:82%
Wow! What a beautiful church.

690
01:07:54.458 --> 01:07:55.575 line:82%
Let's take a look.

691
01:07:55.788 --> 01:07:58.160 line:82%
Who wants to look
inside a church?

692
01:07:58.583 --> 01:08:00.653 line:82%
Come on, Raj. It's so beautiful.

693
01:08:02.418 --> 01:08:04.294 line:82%
Yes. It's really beautiful.

694
01:08:04.662 --> 01:08:05.708 line:82%
You go and look.

695
01:08:46.750 --> 01:08:48.412 line:82%
- What?
- We'll miss our bus.

696
01:09:24.348 --> 01:09:28.419 line:82%
- Shall we go?
- Let's have tea first.

697
01:09:33.497 --> 01:09:34.711 line:82%
What did you pray for?

698
01:09:35.210 --> 01:09:37.836 line:82%
I don't tell what I ask God.

699
01:09:39.276 --> 01:09:41.708 line:82%
You're sure He'll grant your
wishes?

700
01:09:42.983 --> 01:09:47.002 line:82%
I am sure the pure get what
they ask for.

701
01:09:50.583 --> 01:09:51.917 line:82%
You go ahead. I'll join you.

702
01:09:52.000 --> 01:09:54.169 line:82%
- What's wrong?
- Go! I'm coming.

703
01:10:06.792 --> 01:10:08.919 line:82%
Hi, I'm Raj.

704
01:10:10.710 --> 01:10:13.043 line:82%
I'm sorry I don't know
any prayers.

705
01:10:13.487 --> 01:10:16.127 line:82%
I don't want anything for myself.
I'm very happy.

706
01:10:17.921 --> 01:10:20.043 line:82%
But the girl who was here,
Simran...

707
01:10:21.505 --> 01:10:24.169 line:82%
She's lovely. Goodness itself.

708
01:10:25.285 --> 01:10:27.710 line:82%
Whatever she wants,
please give it to her.

709
01:10:29.209 --> 01:10:31.078 line:82%
Please. Thank you.

710
01:10:42.917 --> 01:10:44.016 line:82%
Where were you?

711
01:10:47.376 --> 01:10:48.462 line:82%
In the church?

712
01:11:00.352 --> 01:11:03.380 line:82%
Half a sugar, a drop of milk
and a little cream.

713
01:11:03.463 --> 01:11:04.792 line:82%
- Your coffee.
- Thank you.

714
01:11:06.380 --> 01:11:08.127 line:82%
Want a postcard to send home?

715
01:11:09.617 --> 01:11:13.544 line:82%
If Pops gets a postcard, he'll think
I've died and gone to heaven.

716
01:11:14.417 --> 01:11:15.918 line:82%
Are you ever serious?

717
01:11:16.001 --> 01:11:19.445 line:82%
Never. And if I ever am,
it'll be just one time.

718
01:11:19.528 --> 01:11:23.419 line:82%
- When will that be?
- When I fall in love with someone.

719
01:11:23.695 --> 01:11:26.694 line:82%
Don't tell me a guy like you
has never been in love.

720
01:11:27.208 --> 01:11:30.794 line:82%
I've had lots of affairs. But love?
Never.

721
01:11:31.592 --> 01:11:33.002 line:82%
Didn't find the right girl.

722
01:11:33.382 --> 01:11:34.809 line:82%
What kind of girl do you want?

723
01:11:36.475 --> 01:11:37.580 line:82%
Shall I tell you?

724
01:11:39.653 --> 01:11:42.876 line:82%
The moment I see that girl...

725
01:11:44.083 --> 01:11:46.876 line:82%
she'll awaken my every
dream and desire.

726
01:11:47.152 --> 01:11:48.297 line:82%
How sweet.

727
01:11:48.703 --> 01:11:50.011 line:82%
It's never happened.

728
01:11:50.862 --> 01:11:54.460 line:82%
But I feel someone I've never
seen or met

729
01:11:55.958 --> 01:11:57.793 line:82%
calls me from behind the clouds.

730
01:11:58.833 --> 01:12:00.863 line:82%
Who knows when the clouds
will part...

731
01:12:01.754 --> 01:12:04.169 line:82%
or when she will appear before me.

732
01:12:08.663 --> 01:12:10.711 line:82%
Has that ever happened to you?

733
01:12:13.300 --> 01:12:16.871 line:82%
Has a complete stranger ever crept
into your thoughts?

734
01:12:18.288 --> 01:12:21.087 line:82%
I've no room in my thoughts
for a stranger.

735
01:12:24.313 --> 01:12:25.899 line:82%
My marriage has been arranged.

736
01:12:31.862 --> 01:12:33.597 line:82%
Your marriage has been arranged?

737
01:12:35.175 --> 01:12:36.515 line:82%
Congratulations!

738
01:12:36.598 --> 01:12:38.261 line:82%
Where does the groom live?
London?

739
01:12:38.628 --> 01:12:40.043 line:82%
No, in India.

740
01:12:40.126 --> 01:12:43.092 line:82%
What does he look like?
Tall? Dark? Handsome...?

741
01:12:43.175 --> 01:12:46.211 line:82%
Don't know. I've never met him.

742
01:12:48.403 --> 01:12:52.420 line:82%
You've never met the man
you're going to marry?

743
01:12:53.042 --> 01:12:54.503 line:82%
I don't need to.

744
01:12:54.792 --> 01:12:58.086 line:82%
Father has met him. He's a
family friend's son.

745
01:12:59.542 --> 01:13:03.586 line:82%
You're willing to spend
the rest of your life...

746
01:13:04.418 --> 01:13:07.211 line:82%
with a man you've never met?

747
01:13:08.583 --> 01:13:10.877 line:82%
A man who is a complete
stranger?

748
01:13:13.000 --> 01:13:14.752 line:82%
It's the tradition of our family.

749
01:13:17.250 --> 01:13:19.610 line:82%
Are you happy about the decision?

750
01:13:31.375 --> 01:13:32.795 line:82%
The train is here.

751
01:13:58.458 --> 01:13:59.627 line:82%
This is nice.

752
01:14:01.417 --> 01:14:02.877 line:82%
Yeah, this is also good.

753
01:14:03.500 --> 01:14:05.171 line:82%
I like this one.

754
01:14:17.250 --> 01:14:19.500 line:82%
Simran, lovely photographs.

755
01:14:19.583 --> 01:14:23.604 line:82%
Send me copies of the pictures.
And your wedding photos.

756
01:14:24.465 --> 01:14:28.138 line:82%
- Aren't you coming?
- Not all that way.

757
01:14:28.417 --> 01:14:32.777 line:82%
- Sheena, you must.
- I'll be there. I was joking.

758
01:14:33.038 --> 01:14:38.100 line:82%
I must meet your husband to see
which idiot you're marrying.

759
01:14:42.026 --> 01:14:43.091 line:82%
Excuse me.

760
01:14:43.458 --> 01:14:44.668 line:82%
This fell.

761
01:14:46.833 --> 01:14:48.336 line:82%
I'll be right back.

762
01:15:22.857 --> 01:15:25.372 line:82%
Why are you looking at me
like that?

763
01:15:26.617 --> 01:15:29.919 line:82%
There's something I want
to tell you, Simran.

764
01:15:31.042 --> 01:15:32.084 line:82%
Go ahead.

765
01:15:34.250 --> 01:15:36.426 line:82%
I've fallen in love with you.

766
01:15:40.542 --> 01:15:42.104 line:82%
I love you, Simran.

767
01:15:55.917 --> 01:15:57.669 line:82%
Look at your face.

768
01:16:00.333 --> 01:16:02.502 line:82%
You thought I was telling
the truth.

769
01:16:04.292 --> 01:16:06.127 line:82%
You're amazing, Simran.

770
01:16:06.417 --> 01:16:09.544 line:82%
You still haven't figured me out.

771
01:16:10.337 --> 01:16:13.919 line:82%
Remember I told you
I've never been serious.

772
01:16:14.410 --> 01:16:17.128 line:82%
- Just look at your face.
- You're just too much.

773
01:16:17.417 --> 01:16:20.419 line:82%
This love business isn't for me.

774
01:16:21.107 --> 01:16:26.223 line:82%
How can a man spend his entire
life with the same girl?

775
01:16:26.306 --> 01:16:29.334 line:82%
There are so many pretty girls
in this world.

776
01:16:29.417 --> 01:16:33.917 line:82%
Some have great eyes, others
have great lips, great hair...

777
01:16:34.000 --> 01:16:35.290 line:82%
...You men are all the same.

778
01:16:35.373 --> 01:16:37.169 line:82%
That's me all over.

779
01:16:37.337 --> 01:16:39.834 line:82%
But you've outsmarted me.

780
01:16:41.667 --> 01:16:45.170 line:82%
You can spend the rest
of your life with a man

781
01:16:46.125 --> 01:16:49.170 line:82%
whose face you've never
even seen.

782
01:16:50.792 --> 01:16:54.003 line:82%
Bravo! That's true love.

783
01:17:01.847 --> 01:17:03.500 line:82%
Well, never mind.

784
01:17:03.583 --> 01:17:06.375 line:82%
But what if you fell in love
with someone else?

785
01:17:06.458 --> 01:17:08.336 line:82%
Imagine you met someone
on this holiday

786
01:17:08.583 --> 01:17:10.347 line:82%
and fell in love with him.

787
01:17:10.430 --> 01:17:15.586 line:82%
Anyone, say me. What if
we fell for each other.

788
01:17:19.333 --> 01:17:20.529 line:82%
What would you do then?

789
01:17:22.042 --> 01:17:25.878 line:82%
Would you still go back and
marry that total stranger?

790
01:17:27.583 --> 01:17:31.502 line:82%
Or would you have the guts
to love me?

791
01:17:34.717 --> 01:17:35.745 line:82%
What would you do?

792
01:17:46.000 --> 01:17:48.419 line:82%
I don't want to miss
the train again.

793
01:17:49.167 --> 01:17:51.044 line:82%
I want us to miss it always.

794
01:17:51.808 --> 01:17:52.811 line:82%
What?

795
01:17:54.184 --> 01:17:55.203 line:82%
Nothing.

796
01:18:00.083 --> 01:18:04.294 line:82%
Raj, if she loves you,
she'll turn around and look.

797
01:18:08.602 --> 01:18:09.616 line:82%
Turn around.

798
01:18:16.413 --> 01:18:17.445 line:82%
Turn.

799
01:18:49.453 --> 01:18:52.586 line:82%
Bye, Ponchi. I'll give you a call.

800
01:18:53.208 --> 01:18:57.294 line:82%
See you, Rocky. I'll call you.
Bye, Sheena.

801
01:19:05.208 --> 01:19:06.252 line:82%
This is it.

802
01:19:07.408 --> 01:19:08.567 line:82%
Back in London.

803
01:19:10.042 --> 01:19:11.625 line:82%
How the month flew by!

804
01:19:14.125 --> 01:19:16.292 line:82%
Thank you for everything.

805
01:19:17.917 --> 01:19:20.458 line:82%
- It's all right.
- Friends?

806
01:19:34.526 --> 01:19:37.161 line:82%
- Thanks, see you.
- Bye.

807
01:19:37.924 --> 01:19:41.695 line:82%
Raj, you didn't give me
your address.

808
01:19:42.208 --> 01:19:44.592 line:82%
I'll send you a wedding invite.
Will you come?

809
01:19:47.922 --> 01:19:49.918 line:82%
No, I won't come.

810
01:20:18.249 --> 01:20:21.127 line:82%
I don't know what has

811
01:20:22.375 --> 01:20:25.085 line:82%
come over my heart

812
01:20:30.250 --> 01:20:33.419 line:82%
I had it here with me

813
01:20:36.775 --> 01:20:39.713 line:82%
Now it's gone missing

814
01:20:40.167 --> 01:20:42.822 line:82%
I don't know what has

815
01:20:42.905 --> 01:20:47.382 line:82%
come over my heart

