819
01:20:57.998 --> 01:21:02.384 line:82%
come over my heart

820
01:21:03.043 --> 01:21:09.694 line:82%
I had it here with me.
Now it's gone missing

821
01:21:09.992 --> 01:21:13.835 line:82%
Oh, darling, you've fallen in love

822
01:21:14.875 --> 01:21:18.669 line:82%
Deny it a hundred times
if you must

823
01:21:28.915 --> 01:21:33.106 line:82%
Sweet love, this is what
love is all about

824
01:22:22.250 --> 01:22:26.671 line:82%
You didn't turn around
and look at me

825
01:22:27.000 --> 01:22:30.545 line:82%
I waited for a while

826
01:22:31.742 --> 01:22:36.462 line:82%
I felt like stopping you
from leaving

827
01:22:36.833 --> 01:22:40.212 line:82%
but you were already gone

828
01:22:40.875 --> 01:22:42.878 line:82%
What is happening?

829
01:22:43.419 --> 01:22:45.575 line:82%
I don't know

830
01:22:45.658 --> 01:22:47.959 line:82%
Why is my heart

831
01:22:48.042 --> 01:22:49.794 line:82%
so crazed?

832
01:22:50.750 --> 01:22:54.544 line:82%
Oh, darling, you've fallen in love

833
01:22:55.542 --> 01:22:59.545 line:82%
Deny it a hundred times
if you must

834
01:23:48.376 --> 01:23:52.669 line:82%
Oh time, slow down, stay awhile

835
01:23:53.125 --> 01:23:57.215 line:82%
Go back to days gone past

836
01:23:57.917 --> 01:24:02.336 line:82%
The place where I left my heart

837
01:24:02.875 --> 01:24:06.586 line:82%
is far behind me now

838
01:24:06.959 --> 01:24:11.378 line:82%
- Where am I?
- Where are you?

839
01:24:11.725 --> 01:24:15.961 line:82%
- What is this...
- ... Magic?

840
01:24:16.583 --> 01:24:21.045 line:82%
Oh, darling, you've fallen in love

841
01:24:21.628 --> 01:24:26.088 line:82%
Deny it a hundred times
if you must

842
01:24:35.667 --> 01:24:40.503 line:82%
Sweet love, this is what
love is about

843
01:25:15.875 --> 01:25:21.587 line:82%
What has come over my heart?

844
01:25:27.069 --> 01:25:32.377 line:82%
I had it here with me

845
01:25:33.960 --> 01:25:37.333 line:82%
Now it's gone missing

846
01:25:58.293 --> 01:26:01.377 line:82%
Ma, remember that dream
in my diary?

847
01:26:02.857 --> 01:26:06.294 line:82%
The face I saw in the palm
of my hand?

848
01:26:07.535 --> 01:26:09.911 line:82%
The one I wanted to meet.

849
01:26:11.333 --> 01:26:13.956 line:82%
I met him, Ma. He came to me.

850
01:26:14.910 --> 01:26:18.961 line:82%
What? What are you saying?

851
01:26:19.847 --> 01:26:24.878 line:82%
Yes, Ma. When I left home,
I could see the future clearly.

852
01:26:25.617 --> 01:26:28.836 line:82%
I wanted to live a lifetime
in a month.

853
01:26:29.763 --> 01:26:32.545 line:82%
Then go back to my own country

854
01:26:32.888 --> 01:26:35.836 line:82%
and get married to a total stranger.

855
01:26:36.667 --> 01:26:38.920 line:82%
I had made peace with destiny, Ma.

856
01:26:40.667 --> 01:26:44.003 line:82%
How could I have guessed
this would happen?

857
01:26:45.817 --> 01:26:47.545 line:82%
He entered my life like a storm.

858
01:26:47.875 --> 01:26:50.753 line:82%
And like a falling leaf
I flew with him.

859
01:26:54.458 --> 01:26:58.420 line:82%
I once read that love could be
all sorts of things.

860
01:26:58.958 --> 01:27:00.544 line:82%
But I never understood it.

861
01:27:01.625 --> 01:27:05.922 line:82%
Not even when he held my hand
for the first time.

862
01:27:06.625 --> 01:27:08.669 line:82%
I spent so much time with him.

863
01:27:09.628 --> 01:27:11.086 line:82%
I still didn't get it.

864
01:27:12.288 --> 01:27:16.463 line:82%
But today at the station when he
was leaving...

865
01:27:17.333 --> 01:27:19.503 line:82%
I suddenly realized

866
01:27:20.667 --> 01:27:24.420 line:82%
that I would never see him again.

867
01:27:25.583 --> 01:27:29.586 line:82%
I kept looking back
as he was walking away.

868
01:27:30.292 --> 01:27:31.690 line:82%
I wanted to stop him.

869
01:27:31.773 --> 01:27:33.252 line:82%
Say something.

870
01:27:34.167 --> 01:27:35.544 line:82%
Hear him.

871
01:27:37.333 --> 01:27:38.669 line:82%
He didn't stop.

872
01:27:39.752 --> 01:27:43.045 line:82%
But I understood that's what
love is all about.

873
01:27:44.188 --> 01:27:46.752 line:82%
Now he is in my every dream.

874
01:27:49.227 --> 01:27:51.754 line:82%
I don't know whether
he loves me or not.

875
01:27:52.398 --> 01:27:55.835 line:82%
All I know is that...
he is my life.

876
01:27:57.187 --> 01:27:58.919 line:82%
I can't belong to someone else.

877
01:27:59.458 --> 01:28:01.387 line:82%
I love him, Ma. I really...

878
01:28:16.000 --> 01:28:17.209 line:82%
Oh, you're up!

879
01:28:17.292 --> 01:28:22.628 line:82%
Simi and I were chatting.
I didn't realize the time.

880
01:28:39.167 --> 01:28:43.794 line:82%
I asked you not to betray my trust.

881
01:28:46.542 --> 01:28:48.419 line:82%
I made you promise.

882
01:28:50.167 --> 01:28:51.543 line:82%
But you deceived me.

883
01:28:52.242 --> 01:28:53.292 line:82%
No, Father.

884
01:28:54.685 --> 01:28:56.221 line:82%
I won't hear a word!

885
01:28:59.042 --> 01:29:03.914 line:82%
Pack your bags. We're leaving
for India tomorrow.

886
01:29:05.917 --> 01:29:07.318 line:82%
For good.

887
01:29:13.167 --> 01:29:14.627 line:82%
Let her cry.

888
01:29:15.750 --> 01:29:18.627 line:82%
She gave her fate those tears.

889
01:29:19.583 --> 01:29:23.669 line:82%
She'll learn how to stop them.
Let her cry.

890
01:29:54.162 --> 01:29:55.627 line:82%
Good evening.

891
01:29:56.875 --> 01:29:57.961 line:82%
Beer?

892
01:30:01.000 --> 01:30:03.419 line:82%
- What's the girl's name?
- Simran.

893
01:30:05.625 --> 01:30:07.211 line:82%
What girl, Pops?

894
01:30:08.750 --> 01:30:12.211 line:82%
The one you're looking for
in the face of the moon.

895
01:30:12.542 --> 01:30:15.959 line:82%
You know me, I never fall
for one girl.

896
01:30:16.042 --> 01:30:20.167 line:82%
Oh, I forgot. Some have great lips
others have great eyes.

897
01:30:20.375 --> 01:30:22.252 line:82%
- Exactly...
- ...Exactly.

898
01:30:24.292 --> 01:30:26.711 line:82%
- Where does she live?
- Who, Pops?

899
01:30:28.542 --> 01:30:29.586 line:82%
Simran.

900
01:30:35.833 --> 01:30:36.877 line:82%
I don't know.

901
01:30:38.792 --> 01:30:40.128 line:82%
What's she like?

902
01:30:41.208 --> 01:30:42.544 line:82%
Very lovely.

903
01:30:44.833 --> 01:30:46.033 line:82%
What's the problem?

904
01:30:47.722 --> 01:30:51.878 line:82%
The problem is... she's about
